## Overview

This is an MCP (Model Context Protocol) server built with Go using the [mcp-go](https://github.com/mark3labs/mcp-go) SDK.

## Prerequisites

- Go 1.21 or higher
- Git

## Installation

```bash
# Install dependencies
go mod download

# Build the server
go build -o <%= name %> ./cmd/server
```

## Running the Server

<% if (transport === 'stdio') { %>
